Sidney Blackmer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sidney_Blackmer 0 Sidney Alderman Blackmer (July 13, 1895 – October 6, 1973) was an American actor who appeared in dozens of movies between 1914 and 1971, usually in major supporting roles. He was also a major Broadway performer.
